    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process or activity of preparing beer from barley or other grains. The brewing process can be divided into four steps: mashing, separating, boiling and fermentation. Different approaches to the brewing process lead to variation in beers and beer types.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
